'''''Blue Birthday''''' ({{Korean|블루버스데이||rr=beu-lu-beo-seu-de-i}}) waa taxane shabakad oo Koonfur Kuuriya ah oo ay soo saartay [[Naver]] hoosaad [[Playlist Studio]].<ref>[https://www.hancinema.net/new-drama-blue-birthday-150483.html <nowiki>[New Drama] "Blue Birthday"</nowiki>].</ref> Waxaa agaasime ka ah Park Dan-hee oo ay isla qoreen Goo So-yeon iyo Moon Won-young, jilayaasha taxanaha [[Yeri|Kim Ye-rim]] sida Oh Ha-rin iyo [[Hongseok|Yang Hong-seok]] sida Ji Seo-jun. Taxanihu wuxuu ku saabsan yahay Oh Ha-Rin, wuxuu dib ugu noqdaa sawirro qarsoodi ah oo uu ka tagay jacaylkeedii ugu horreeyay, kaasoo ku dhintay dhalashadeedii 10 sano ka hor. Waxaa la sii daayay 23 -kii Luulyo iyada oo loo sii mariyay [[Naver TV]] iyo [[Tencent Video|WeTV]] waxaana la sii daayaa Jimce kasta iyo Sabtida markay tahay 19:00 (KST). Waxaa la sii daayay 6 -dii Agosto iyada oo loo marayo [[YouTube]]-ka dhagaystayaasha caalamiga ah. Si kastaba ha noqotee, waxaa heli kara oo keliya dhagaystayaasha ka socda Koonfur Kuuriya.

== Qoraal kooban ==
Taxanaha ayaa ka sheekeynaya sheekada Oh Ha-Rin (Kim Ye-rim), oo u safreysa waqtiyadii hore sawirro qarsoodi ah oo uu ka tagay jaceylkeedii ugu horreeyay, Ji Seo-Jun (Yang Hong-seok). Tan iyo markii ay sideed jirsadeen, waxay ahaayeen saaxiibo isku dhow, laakiin wuxuu isdilay dhalashadeedii toban sano ka hor. Dhalashada 28aad, Ha-rin waxay heshaa fursad qaali ah hadiyad ahaan;  isagoo adeegsanaya sawirro dahsoon oo uu ka tagay Seo-Jun, Ha-Rin wuxuu dib ugu noqdaa maalintaas hore si uu u ogaado sababta uu u doortay inuu dhinto oo naftiisa badbaadiyo.

